I made a [Drafts](https://getdrafts.com) [custom action](https://docs.getdrafts.com/actions/) that looks at the current [workspace](https://docs.getdrafts.com/docs/drafts/workspaces), grabs the [tags](https://docs.getdrafts.com/docs/drafts/tagging), and applies them to a new draft that is opened in the editor. It also supplies a keyboard shortcut:

